'''半乳糖腦苷脂'''（galactocerebroside、galactosylceramide）是一種包含由"部分1-羥基"(1-hydroxyl moiety)[[半乳糖|半乳糖]]殘基之[[神經酰胺|神經酰胺]](Ceramide)所組成的[[脑苷脂|脑苷脂]]。

半乳糖是由[[半乳糖基神經酰胺酶|半乳糖基神經酰胺酶]](Galactosylceramidase)所裂解。

半乳糖腦苷脂是腦裡之[[少突神經膠質細胞|少突神經膠質細胞]](oligodendrocyte)的標記物，且無論它們是否形成[[髓磷脂|髓磷脂]]。<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Galactocerebroside is a specific cell-surface antigenic marker for oligodendrocytes in culture|url=https://www.nature.com/articles/274813a0|last=Raff|first=Martin C.|last2=Mirsky|first2=Rhona|date=1978-08|journal=Nature|issue=5673|doi=10.1038/274813a0|volume=274|pages=813–816|language=en|issn=1476-4687|last3=Fields|first3=K. L.|last4=Lisak|first4=Robert P.|last5=Dorfman|first5=Susan H.|last6=Silberberg|first6=Donald H.|last7=Gregson|first7=N. A.|last8=Leibowitz|first8=Sidney|last9=Kennedy|first9=Mary C.|access-date=2021-11-10|archive-date=2021-11-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211110135752/https://www.nature.com/articles/274813a0|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|title=Galactocerebroside is expressed by non-myelin-forming Schwann cells in situ.|url=https://rupress.org/jcb/article/101/3/1135/28276/Galactocerebroside-is-expressed-by|last=Jessen|first=K R|last2=Morgan|first2=L|date=1985-09-01|journal=The Journal of Cell Biology|issue=3|doi=10.1083/jcb.101.3.1135|volume=101|pages=1135–1143|language=en|issn=0021-9525|pmc=PMC2113740|pmid=3897245|last3=Brammer|first3=M|last4=Mirsky|first4=R|access-date=2021-11-10|archive-date=2021-11-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211110133411/https://rupress.org/jcb/article/101/3/1135/28276/Galactocerebroside-is-expressed-by|dead-url=no}}</ref>

